Overview:
This library uses the Prebid SDK, only as a dependency and is connected using Gradle via
mavenCentral. All Prebid Samples are copied in their original form and correspond to the version
specified in gradle/libs.versions.toml#prebid. Any changes made to the files are reflected in
the following changelog.

Changelog:
- ([Example PrebidDemoJava/build.gradle](https://github.com/audienzz/audienzz-android-sdk/Example/PrebidDemoJava/build.gradle))
- ([Example PrebidDemoKotlin/build.gradle](https://github.com/audienzz/audienzz-android-sdk/Example/PrebidDemoKotlin/build.gradle))
- ([Example PrebidInternalTestApp/build.gradle](https://github.com/audienzz/audienzz-android-sdk/Example/PrebidInternalTestApp/build.gradle))
- ([Example PrebidInternalTestApp/utils/DemoItemProvider](https://github.com/audienzz/audienzz-android-sdk/Example/PrebidInternalTestApp/src/java/org/prebid/mobile/renderingtestapp/utils/DemoItemProvider.kt))
- ([Example PrebidInternalTestApp/AdActivity](https://github.com/audienzz/audienzz-android-sdk/Example/PrebidInternalTestApp/src/java/org/prebid/mobile/renderingtestapp/AdActivity.kt))

You can read more about changes in files in the header of each file.
